headline.main: Canadiens Pound Rangers 4-1, Extend Winning Streak to 5
headline.print_headline: Canadiens Pound Rangers 4-1, Extend Winning Streak to 5

lead_paragraph: Carey Price and the Montreal Canadiens showed off their resurgent form under coach Claude Julien with a big Eastern Conference win.
